        <h2>Small code-golf like challenges</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="codetta-panel-body codetta-intro-body">
      <p>
        Codettas are small F-flat-minor code-golf like challenges with fixed expected output. Many mirror
        <code>code.golf</code> holes, with a few repo-defined variants.
      </p>
      <p>
        Leaderboard rank is based on optimized compiled <code>.ffb</code> byte count, not source length.
        Output has to match the expected result before the byte score matters.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
